transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello. Ha, photos add kar diye photos aapke. Do ka mujhe provide kar dena bas wooden tray aur wooden gift box ka.
Customer: Chalo mai bas check kar leta hu na.
Executive: Ha, ek baar check kar lo aap. Price dal diya na aapne? Sara sara price dalna hai, description aapke end se dalna hai. Ki Google se lega kyuki sare me same description hai.
Customer: To wo bhi aapke end se dalega. Description jo hai na, ha ha sare product me same hai. Google se lenge to wo wala galat ho jayega. To wo bhi aapke end se dalega. Photos maine dal diye leke edit crop karke, badha ke photos maine dal diye.
Executive: Do ka photos mujhe de dena apne end se. Do ka photo nahi dal pa rahe the wooden tray aur wooden gift box rah gaya. Do product rah gaya bas.
Customer: Mai dal deta hu na.
Executive: Thik hai. Lage kuch mujhe batao. Maine dal diya hai. Aur price dal dena. Price aapke end se dalega. Price to mujhe pata nahi hai.
Customer: Thik hai.
Executive: Nahi nahi price vagera mai dal de raha hu abhi.
Executive: Bas ek feedback aayega sir usme bas yes kar dena wo mere liye hota hai. Thik hai ki maine aapko response diya ki nahi.
Customer: Thik hai, thik hai aane do feedback aane do.
Executive: Thik hai. Ha, ek mail aayega usko aap yes karke aap de dena. Thik hai. Mail open hai aapka?
Customer: Ha ha open hai open hai.
Executive: Ek baar mail open karna apna.
Executive: Kahi bhi lage sir aap mujhe batao mujhe add karne ya kuch bhi karne koi problem nahi hai aap isliye pareshan na ho matlab chizo ko lekar. Thik hai.
Customer: Sir pareshan kya mere ko bas business chahiye aur kuch nahi chahiye.
Executive: Sir abhi saat din hue hai thoda patient aapko rakhna padega. Kyuki fir se ye start hoti hai chize.
Customer: Wo thoda patient kya mai rakhta agar mai naya banda hota to magar kya ek saal se hu na mai to patient hone se fir baat nahi rehti.
Executive: Sir aap naya nahi hai par aapne band kara diya tha na beech me. Problem to ye hui na beech me.
Customer: Aise sir wo band kara diya tha ek mahine ke liye band hua tha bhaiya wapis wapis chalu karwaenge na.
Executive: Band ho jate hai na. To matlab listing to band ho jati hai na. Wahi to mai bol raha hu ki jaise jaise listing aapki banti hai na to ho jayegi. Pareshani ke liye ekdam mat aao.
Customer: Aaya nahi mere paas.
Executive: Ha?
Customer: Ek dekh
Customer: Aaya nahi mere paas.
Executive: Feedback nahi aaya. Dekh rahe ho aap? Bolna mail apna kholna.
Customer: Mail khula hua hai mera.
Executive: Do ek minute.
Executive: Aur dekhna bhi aaya hoga aapke paas.
Executive: Dekhiye ho jata kya feedback aaya tha fir kya mere company ke number se phone jane lagta hai ye sab chize. Isliye personal number de rakha hai aapko kahi lage mujhe to call kar liya karo ekdam.
Customer: Thik hai sir thik hai. Satisfied kar diya.
Executive: Dekhna aaya hoga.
Executive: Kuch hua comment to mere liye.
Customer: Hain?
Executive: Kuch nahi. Kar diya maine check karna. Aur do ka rah gaya maine aapko saaf bata diya do ka raha photo aap de do photo jo hai fir wo Google se wo sahi photo aa nahi rahi thi pixel uske jara bhi tray wali aur gift box ki. To mujhe de dena mai dal dunga. Thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai. Ye suggestion mang raha hai. Thank you for your valuable feedback.
Executive: Suggestion jo hai de do mere liye kuch comment hoga to kar dena aap jaisi aapki ichcha lage.
Customer: Chalo thik hai mai karta hu na.
